JBox2D
================================================================================

The package com.codename1.gaming.physics.box2d is a derived work of JBox2D
(https://github.com/jbox2d/jbox2d), a Java port of Erin Catto's Box2D physics
engine. The sources have been repackaged from org.jbox2d into
com.codename1.gaming.physics.box2d and lightly adapted for the Codename One
virtual machines (replacing StrictMath with Math and removing GWT specific
emulation), with no algorithmic changes. The original copyright and license
notices are retained in each source file.

